Rinchi-CPlusPlus-Preprocessor version 0.02
==========================================

A C++ preprocessor that provides results through an XML SAX interface. It
implements full macro expansion capabilities and all standard preprocessing
directives. It also provides an alternative to complex conditional compilation,
use on code.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Carp
Exporter
XSLoader

flex
bison
popt

